sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Engine
    participant R as Red Agents
    participant D as Deconfliction
    participant H as Hardening
    participant B as Blue Agents
    participant T as AuditTrace

    E->>E: TICK_START
    loop Each Red agent
        E->>R: perceive + decide + act
        R->>D: register target
        R->>H: attack / absorb
        R->>T: record trace
    end
    loop Each Blue agent
        E->>B: perceive + decide + act
        B->>D: register target
        B->>H: harden
        B->>T: record trace
    end
    E->>E: TICK_COMPLETE